name: AudioFilePacketTableInfo
desc: Contains information about the number of valid frames in a file and where they begin and end.

items.name: init(mNumberValidFrames: Int64, mPrimingFrames: Int32, mRemainderFrames: Int32)
var mNumberValidFrames: Int64
items.desc: The number of valid frames in the file.

items.name: var mPrimingFrames: Int32
items.desc: The number of invalid frames at the beginning of the file.

items.name: var mRemainderFrames: Int32
items.desc: The number of invalid frames at the end of the file.
